CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 5, 2010

[Cite as 05/05/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-1893.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2010-0269. State ex rel. Morris v. Court of Appeals, Tenth Appellate Dist.
